parameters: \nc<???>She won't wake up... What should we do?

\nc<???>Since you're going to shower anyway, just splash some water
on her.

\bustMoveTo[2, -100, 720, 30]\nc<Senpai>Saki, wake up already. The manager is having trouble because
of you.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Ugh, is everything over? What about the guests...

\nc<Senpai>They've long since gone home. To think you fainted on your
own partway through. Be thankful there were no complaints.

\nc<Saki>But it was really tough... Senpai, you're terrible for
recommending this!

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Don't talk like that. It couldn't be helped because of the
executive.

\nc<Senpai>Yes. The executive who developed this attraction came by
earlier... It was a hassle because they sulked all day when
there were no users.

\nc<Senpai>Saki, you were needed because you were in charge of the
testing too. Good work. I'll treat you to dinner, so get up
quickly.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Dinner... That means overtime, doesn't it? Please let me
leave work instead of dinner...

\nc<Senpai>There's a lot of work today, so no way♥ The executive is
also waiting for your work report. Make sure to write only
the good things, okay?
